        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your magnetic foot orb picks up loose metal objects that you can retrieve later. Whenever you leave a square, you can pick up one unattended object of 1 Bulk or less that is mostly made out of metal with your foot orb. Your foot orb can hold 4 Bulk of items, and the first 2 Bulk of these items don't count against your Bulk limits. These items are considered stowed and must be drawn in order to be used.</p>"
